<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Ontology> .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://creativecommons.org/ns#license> "http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/" .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Bart Gajderowicz (bart.gajderowicz@usu.edu" .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Keith Dugas (keith.dugas@secours.ai)" .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/creator> "Paul Knowles (paul@secours.ai)" .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "\nCore Domain Ontology (CDO) is a semantic model developed to support the Informatics Domain Model IDM. \nThe CDO is structured around five central nodes: objects, events, concepts, actions, and domain, which \nunderpin various aspects of planning, reasoning, and execution in digital systems. It enables \ndecentralized data representation, transformation, and alignment. \n                                " .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2025-03-20"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-03-11"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date> .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/rights> "Copyright @ 2026 Paul Knowles, Bart Gajderowicz, Keith Dugas" .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Core Domain Ontology" .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespacePrefix> "cdo" .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/preferredNamespaceUri> "https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#" .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Core Domain Ontology" .
<https://onto.colossi.network/cdo#CoreDomainOntology> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#versionInfo> "\nVersion 1 March 11, 2026" .
